          "text": "A\nname used at this time for the Andaman Islands, so this is likely a misnaming\nof an island. “These\nmen are idolaters who live like beasts. There is an abundance of all aromatics\nthere. The men have deformed heads, like the heads of dogs.” This map also adds\nin a depiction of them as cannibals. [7]"
