        "text": {
          "headline": "Java Major: Java",
          "text": "At\nthe north of the island is identified a “forest of nutmeg.” Other things listed as\nfound on the island include “pepper, nutmeg, spikenard, galingale, cloves, and\nan abundance of other kinds of spices” as well as “forest of pepper” The island\nis\ndescribed as being\nthree thousand miles in circumference, the people “idolators” and the king as\nsomeone who “pays tribute to no one.” [8]"
